<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM5.6.6">
<l>tañciṉattait tavirttaṭaintār tavaneṟiyai tariyātu</l>
<l>kañcaṉaikkoṉ ṟaṉṟulaka muṇṭumiḻnta kaṟpakattai</l>
<l>veñciṉatta koṭuntoḻilōṉ vicaiyuruvai yacaivitta</l>
<l>vañciṟaippuṭ pākaṉaiyāṉ kaṇṭatuteṉ ṉaraṅkattē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>My beholding of [the one who is] the path of penance</l>
<l rend="indent">of those who seek refuge, having restrained their anger,</l>
<l>The [one who is] the giving-tree who, having killed Kaṁsa,</l>
<l rend="indent">being intolerant [of him], having eaten the world and disgorged [it],</l>
<l>The rider on the fine-winged bird who drove off the swift figure</l>
<l>Of the one whose function is severe, angry, and cruel,</l>
<l rend="indent">was in Araṅkam of the South.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
